        <h1 class="about-title">About Us</h1>

        <p class="about-subtitle">
          DriveX is a modern land-vehicle dealership platform designed to make buying and selling vehicles easier than ever.
        </p>

        <div class="about-content">

          <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>
              DriveX was created with the idea of building a simple, intuitive, and reliable platform for vehicle enthusiasts and everyday drivers. 
              We focus on offering a clear and professional space where users can explore, compare, and discover cars and motorcycles in a fast and comfortable way.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-section">
            <h2>What We Do</h2>
            <p>
              Our platform allows users to browse detailed vehicle listings with complete technical information, high-quality images, 
              and transparent pricing. Whether you are looking for a family car, a sports vehicle, or a powerful bike, DriveX helps you find the perfect match.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
              We aim to modernize the traditional dealership experience by combining technology and simplicity. 
              Our mission is to create a trusted environment where buying and selling vehicles becomes a smooth and enjoyable process for everyone.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
              <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Honest and detailed information for every vehicle.</li>
              <li><strong>Quality:</strong> Professional listings with accurate specifications.</li>
              <li><strong>Trust:</strong> A secure and reliable platform for all users.</li>
              <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> Easy-to-use design focused on user experience.</li>
              <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Constant improvement and new features.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

